  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20090201011723/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/88/" target="_top">sumim</a><a href="/web/20090201011723/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#medal" target="_top"><img src="/web/20090201011723im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/star_gold.png" border=0/></a><a href="/web/20090201011723/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#anomark" target="_top"><img src="/web/20090201011723im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/anomark.png" border=0/></a>

	
